# Dependencies (root pattern alone does not exclude apps/*/node_modules)
**/node_modules

# Next.js / build outputs (recreated in image)
**/.next
**/dist
*.tsbuildinfo

# Expo / React Native — never send host native build trees into the context
**/.expo
**/ios/build
**/ios/Pods
**/ios/*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata
**/android/app/build
**/android/build
**/android/.gradle
**/android/local.properties
apps/mobile/android/*

# Caches & tooling noise
**/.turbo
**/.cache
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
.git
.DS_Store
*.log

# Secrets (keep example templates)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
